ine+Sheet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F25%2F25%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_sou=
rce=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ) about today=E2=80=99s co-=
ed centenary show, which people seemed to really like. (And not just Baguet=
te queen Sarah Jessica Parker, who sat front row.) As for Ros=E2=80=99s pro=
spects, Louis Vuitton is the training ground for LVMH execs, so it=E2=80=99=
s not far-fetched that
he=E2=80=99d get an upgrade at some point. The company did not comment on t=
