Good Girl, the iconic Carolina Herrera fragrance, recently surpassed Chanel=
=E2=80=99s Chance as
the world=E2=80=99s best-selling women=E2=80=99s perfume. An inside look at=
 how Puig, the brand=E2=80=99s Spanish owner, leveraged social media and sa=
vvy marketing to dethrone a legend.

Rachel Strugatz ( https://puck.news/author/rachel-strugatz/?utm_campaign=3D=
Line+Sheet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F26%2F25%29&utm_content=3DLine+Sheet+-+SUBSC=
