global corporate workforce, or about 150 jobs. I suspect that executives ac=
ross the newly formed group=E2=80=94which includes Saks Fifth Avenue, Neima=
n Marcus, and Bergdorf Goodman=E2=80=94saw this coming. At the very least, =
they should have. With any merger, there are redundancies.<br/><br/>In a to=
wn hall meeting on Wednesday afternoon, Metrick addressed a few specific is=
